{"tid":345063,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（垃圾廢青遊記）張機票好貴架！東西南歐Chur盡四十幾日","createTime":"2017-08-02T17:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T03:47:56.000Z","uid":51200,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d0f7be3937b397d1b4f05c4a77bd985ed230c8","tid":345063,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:45:38.000Z","msg":"第一次係連登打遊記，請多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為一直好想去遠d地方，<br />\n所以我呢個廢青就同左位師兄約實係 6丶7月去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁因為位師兄之後有野做，所以大部分留係巴爾幹半島同波蘭既時間，<br />\n都係me alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係連登開po係因為之前應承過d巴絲打，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於今次去既地方之前都未去過，所以希望大家唔好恥笑得太大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題我會盡力答，同樣地答錯左麻煩巴絲打手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b08fdcd8c4e673c4dbf1b521fbc7f90729a136d","tid":345063,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:58:20.000Z","msg":"咁首先講返少少資料先，<br />\n因睇左咁多遊記，都知好多人會問：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日期：6月頭至7月尾<br />\n相機：絕大多數用Rx100m5既自動Mode（唔識影相）<br />\n少部分用iphone，<br />\n所有係連登既相全部直出，無P無雞精特效Effect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預算:~30000HKD<br />\nA交通連保險：~12700HKD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nB住宿：~7650HKD<br />\nC其他洗費：~9700HKD<br />\n<br />\n行程:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/015254_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F015254_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=9484f3ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-= one way / += round trip<br />\n6月<br />\n11 Hk-多哈轉機<br />\n12 Warsaw<br />\n13 Warsaw - Barcelona <br />\n14 Barcelona <br />\n15 Barcelona -Madrid <br />\n16 Madrid<br />\n17 Madrid -Lisbon<br />\n18 Lisbon<br />\n19 Lisbon -Napoli<br />\n20 Napoli <br />\n21 Napoli<br />\n22 Napoli -Florence <br />\n23 Florence<br />\n24 Florence -Pisa -Cinque Terre<br />\n25 Cinque Terre<br />\n26 Cinque Terre-Venice<br />\n27 Venice <br />\n28 Venice- Ljubljana<br />\n29 Ljubljana 湖+洞+城<br />\n30 Ljubljana 湖+洞+城<br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n7月<br />\n1 Ljublijana-Zagreb<br />\n2 Zagreb -16湖<br />\n3 16湖-split<br />\n4 Split-Hvar<br />\n5 Hvar-Dubrovnik<br />\n6 Dubrovnik<br />\n7 Dubrovnik-Sarajevo<br />\n8 Sarajevo <br />\n9 Sarajevo-Mostar<br />\n10 Mostar-Podgorica (蒙特)<br />\n11 Podgorica+Kotor/Budva<br />\n12 Podgorica- Athens<br />\n13 Athens <br />\n14 Athens-Mykonos <br />\n15 Mykonos +Delos<br />\n16 Mykonos-Santorini <br />\n17 Santorini +火山+Oia+Fira<br />\n18 Santorini-Athens<br />\n19 Athens(-Warsaw<br />\n20 Warsaw-Krakow<br />\n21 krakow<br />\n22 Krakow-Warsaw <br />\n23 Warsaw-多哈(Join 1 day tour)<br />\n24 多哈-Hk<br />\n<br />\n其實呢次係我第二次去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次係咁(有機會嘅話再出遊記, 29日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) :<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/015616_22a1747dbc758c161ef5010c44dd775f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F015616_22a1747dbc758c161ef5010c44dd775f.png&h=29e448e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩次重叠 : <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/015640_f6dc964b6553fc85b0daddf94df09ed5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F015640_f6dc964b6553fc85b0daddf94df09ed5.png&h=1a5713fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後再去就應該去北歐英國俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d822a28d3c8390162cfbbcfd3b2f7e07324541bd","tid":345063,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T18:02:54.000Z","msg":"今晚開左個頭，訓教先，聽日再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2584e94d0f90cade20b21b02f395a1bb8b686e5","tid":345063,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T00:40:48.000Z","msg":"Skip Andalusia Spain <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9e22b856f07c9faea1be468fed00c326683b53","tid":345063,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"來回都係坐Qatar，而且夾埋訓左兩晚機場<br />\n不過Skip哂，直接寫歐洲Day 1算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 : 華沙，波蘭 (Warsaw, Poland)<br />\n其實波蘭暫時係我最鍾意嘅歐洲國家黎，<br />\n因為第一物價平，第二啲人守規矩丶安全，<br />\n第三地方乾淨，第四天氣叫做舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFor example:<br />\n好似Krakow咁，<br />\n有m記有大型商場，<br />\n交通又方便(Train/Bus station+Airport)，<br />\n忙中帶靜又有歷史痕跡真係好岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返Warsaw先，<br />\n講真，呢個城市對我黎講算係好好既第一站，<br />\n之後既旅程，真係大部分國家都要不停Chur盡去行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呢度，落機之後休息下，<br />\nhea下，行下Warsaw個好細既＂舊＂城區，<br />\n咁就一日了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ejbr1fgk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fejbr1fgk&h=98cc0a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行行下，落雨落狗屎<br />\n明明好大雨，<br />\n把遮吹到就嚟散開<br />\n但係啲鬼佬同鬼婆都係唔興開遮既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁呢個時候當然係要立即閃入間雪糕店入邊食雪糕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dbgaol4m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdbgaol4m&h=7a9fbdfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://holland.pk/tykgjfbc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftykgjfbc&h=8f53b822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/190712_fe1e41494b45acfdd6aec9126bce9226.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F190712_fe1e41494b45acfdd6aec9126bce9226.JPG&h=f56d110b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f78d2838da13dd5202a032703ff3043d07f67be6","tid":345063,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Skip Andalusia Spain <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係睇住本叫《旅行之步方》既旅行書去Plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為係本雞精書所以未必有齊哂所有旅遊城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過本書幾有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ff82f5964d9fea7f18a778d52496c091ede72c","tid":345063,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"屋企人叫到，又要食飯先，食完再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1266c3fc6c5169cef999e63186b378d898472cc","tid":345063,"uid":11903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"e6ab808d29c71748f16b3191b71873ebe1733123","tid":345063,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持</blockquote><br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374dd314cc88c34a2cde340502d68ea9dc90272e","tid":345063,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"strong post lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d343957db658914b18c4d143cb5402f73c11fe","tid":345063,"uid":86433,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T17:42:33.000Z","msg":"個飯食佐6日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcf2d16ce401283aa7e888edce8edfbd201182e","tid":345063,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個飯食佐6日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}